				<productText readOnly="true">
					<description lang="en">FileDescription=EDS for MovingCap turnTRACK MC 349|EdsVersion=1|FileRevison=1|RevisionNum=1|Comments=Device description for MovingCap turnTRACK MC349 ETH
and base file valid for all other MovingCap Ethernet TCP/IP drives:
MovingCap turnTRACK (MC632/634/636 ETH, MCN23 ETH) 
MovingCap flatTRACK (MCFLAT ETH, flatTRACK 100-650, FATtrack 200)
MovingCap shortTRACK (MCSHORT ETH shortTRACK 046) 
MovingCap pushTRACK (pushTRACK 45S100 - 115S240)

For documentation and support see www.movingcap.com


|</description>
				</productText>
